<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GLASS-COLUMN-$ADV09-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COMMENTARY: HI-DEF TV GOES BLURRY
 &HT;    Moving in (k) Commentary and (l) lifestyle categories for
release Sunday, July 9.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
