<HEADLINE>
PROPER FOOD HANDLING PREVENTS PROBLEMS
</HEADLINE>
  (For use after June 8, 2000 by NYTimes News Service clients. A copy
is being transmitted to both food and lifestyle wires.) 
 
 
By ANGELA LEMIRE 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Health officials estimate that more than 85,000 food-borne
illnesses occur during the summer months in Los Angeles County _
about half the cases for the entire year.
</P>
