<SLUG> BC-FILM-SCARYMOVIE-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THERE'S NOT MUCH ABOUT `SCARY'
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By ROBERT PHILPOT 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
