</P>
<P>
   MIDEAST-SUMMIT (Jerusalem) _ Both Ehud Barak and Yasser Arafat
will go into next Tuesday's summit at Camp David with less than a
third of their own people approving, a weakness that many think
will make it difficult for either to offer the concessions that
