<P>
   AMTRAK-FREE-RIDE (Washington) _ Amtrak said Thursday that it
would offer every dissatisfied customer a free repeat trip, even if
the problem was not its fault. The new program is part of Amtrak's
campaign to build ridership and revenue by reducing the number of
disgruntled passengers before Congress cuts off operating subsidies
in 2003. By Matthew L. Wald.
