<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-06 19:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4751 &Cx1f; tth-z
u e BC-FILM-TRIXIE-SPI &LR;      07-06 0530
