BKL-SPARKS-MYSTICS (Inglewood, Calif.) _ The Los Angeles Sparks
face the Washington Mystics at 7:30 p.m. PDT. 
By Kerry Murray/Long Beach Press-Telegram. (Will move on the ``s''
sports file.) 

